# AEM block JS

- Export `export default function decorate(block)` or async equivalent
- Keep decoration resilient to missing rows/cells
- Use `createOptimizedPicture` for content images
- Import from `../../scripts/aem.js` with `.js` extension
- No bundlers, no JSX, no TypeScript in blocks
- Prefer small helpers inside the file over new shared modules unless reused 3+ times
